    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "> The reason the player is also given the building queue is because if it isn't the case then the upgrade tab gets shown to you when deploying your first MCV. \n\nThis would be better fixed by adding a flag to the upgrade queue or MCV so that it doesn't get automatically selected.\n"
