    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Not sure exactly what you mean (adding a new flag or something else), but the deeper issue appears to be that production is only granted once buildup is complete whereas prerequisites are activated immediately. This is why, if you give only the upgrade queue to the player, it is selected first because the upgrades prerequisites are granted immediately thereby filling up the upgrade tab.\n"
