    "updated_at": "2015-12-29T14:16:51Z",
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "The fundamental problem is that the upgrade queue is automatically selected by the game, which we don't want to happen because the upgrade queue is special in that it exists to the side of the regular production / tech / build palette setup.\n\nI'm suggesting that we should just _tell_ the game this instead of relying on a fragile (its not an expected use, so it might break in the future) workaround to trick it into doing what we want.\n"
